About Paradise Communities
Paradise Communities owns and manages six, senior, manufactured home communities located in highly desirable coastal markets of Florida.
We have a strong belief in a company-wide customer focused philosophy much like that found in the hospitality industry.
The senior manufactured home product is a superior “lifestyle” experience for its customers, and everyone in the company is required to serve the “customer first”.
The experience is delivered best when employees adhere to the principle that they must serve the customer or serve someone who is servicing the customer.
Employees throughout the organization are trained to be “fun, friendly and helpful” to not only customers but to associate employees as well.
/blogpost
